ISLAMABAD, Jul 28 (APP):Minister for Energy Hammad Azhar Wednesday said the people of Sialkot rejected those who made anti-Pakistan rhetoric in their drawing room in by election.
Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) won the constituency in 2018 that decided in favor of the PTI after three years, he tweeted.
